---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const breadcrumbList = [{"name": "Home", "url": "https://truejoybirthing.com/"}, {"name": "New Doula Start Here", "url": "https://truejoybirthing.com/new-doula-start-here/"}];
---

<Layout
  title="New Doula Start Here — Build Your Practice"
  description="Starting as a birth doula? Get the tools, templates, and systems to book clients, run client meetings, and grow with confidence."
    canonical="https://truejoybirthing.com/new-doula-start-here/"
    ogImage="/images/og/og-new-doula-start-here.png"
    breadcrumbList={breadcrumbList}
  >

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO — New doula focus
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden curve-bottom pb-4">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-tjb-lavender-100" />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 dot-grid" />

    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-20 md:pt-24 md:pb-28">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 md:gap-16 items-center">
        
        <!-- Left: Headline + CTAs -->
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow mb-4">For New Doulas</p>

          <h1 class="mb-6 text-[2.2rem] md:text-[3rem] leading-[1.12] font-bold text-tjb-charcoal">
            Starting as a Doula? Here's What Nobody Tells You About Building a Real Practice
          </h1>

          <p class="text-lg md:text-[1.125rem] text-tjb-gray leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-xl">
            The certification is just the beginning. The real work is finding clients, running organized sessions, and building systems that don't fall apart when you get busy. Here's how to do it.
          </p>

          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a href="#get-started" class="btn-primary text-center">
              Get the Free Starter Kit
            </a>
            <a href="/birth-plan-template/" class="btn-secondary text-center">
              Get the Free App
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Real doula photo -->
        <div class="relative flex justify-center md:justify-end">
          <div class="w-full max-w-sm rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl shadow-tjb-lavender-300/40">
            <img 
              src="/images/doula-teaching.webp" 
              srcset="/images/responsive/doula-teaching-480w.webp 480w, /images/responsive/doula-teaching-960w.webp 960w, /images/doula-teaching.webp 1024w"
              sizes="(max-width: 480px) 480px, (max-width: 960px) 960px, 1024px"
              alt="Doula teaching expecting parents about birth support" 
              class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
              loading="eager"
              width="1024"
              height="1536"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       THE PROBLEM — Why most new doulas struggle
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="bg-tjb-cream py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="eyebrow mb-4">The Reality</p>
        <div class="w-10 h-0.5 bg-tjb-rose-500 mx-auto mb-6"></div>
        <h2 class="text-[2.25rem] md:text-[2.75rem] leading-[1.15] max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Certification Doesn't Come With a Business
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-tjb-lavender-200/50">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-tjb-rose-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-tjb-rose-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl mb-3">No Clients</h3>
          <p class="text-tjb-gray leading-relaxed">You finished training. You have the heart. But the phone isn't ringing. Where do you even start finding families who need you?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-tjb-lavender-200/50">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-tjb-lavender-200 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-tjb-lavender-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl mb-3">No Systems</h3>
          <p class="text-tjb-gray leading-relaxed">Notebooks, spreadsheets, random apps. Your client info is scattered. You forget follow-ups. You look disorganized even when you're not.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-tjb-lavender-200/50">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-tjb-sage-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-tjb-sage" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl mb-3">No Confidence</h3>
          <p class="text-tjb-gray leading-relaxed">You second-guess your pricing. You freeze in the birth room. You want to serve but you're still figuring out what "professional" looks like.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       SOLUTION — What True Joy Birthing offers
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="bg-tjb-cream-50 py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="eyebrow mb-4">What You Get</p>
        <div class="w-10 h-0.5 bg-tjb-rose-500 mx-auto mb-6"></div>
        <h2 class="text-[2.25rem] md:text-[2.75rem] leading-[1.15] max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          A Practice Starter Kit Built by a Doula Who's Been There
        </h2>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature list with images -->
      <div class="space-y-16">
        <!-- Feature 1 -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
            <img src="/images/online-education.webp" srcset="/images/responsive/online-education-480w.webp 480w, /images/responsive/online-education-960w.webp 960w, /images/online-education.webp 1400w" sizes="(max-width: 480px) 480px, (max-width: 960px) 960px, 1400px" alt="Online doula education and training" class="w-full h-64 object-cover" loading="lazy" width="1400" height="800" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="text-5xl font-bold text-tjb-lavender-400 font-serif">01</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl mt-2 mb-4">Client-Ready Birth Plan Templates</h3>
            <p class="text-tjb-gray leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Don't reinvent the wheel. Use the same birth plan templates Shelbi refined over hundreds of births. Moms understand them. Nurses respect them. You look like the pro you are.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-tjb-gray space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-tjb-rose-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
                <span>Hospital-ready, nurse-friendly format</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-tjb-rose-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
                <span>Covers every stage from induction to postpartum</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-tjb-rose-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
                <span>Editable in the free app — no design skills needed</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 2 -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center md:flex-row-reverse">
          <div class="md:order-2 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
            <img src="/images/virtual-meeting.webp" srcset="/images/responsive/virtual-meeting-480w.webp 480w, /images/responsive/virtual-meeting-960w.webp 960w, /images/virtual-meeting.webp 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 480px) 480px, (max-width: 960px) 960px, 1536px" alt="Virtual doula support meeting" class="w-full h-64 object-cover" loading="lazy" width="1536" height="1024" />
          </div>
          <div class="md:order-1">
            <span class="text-5xl font-bold text-tjb-rose-400 font-serif">02</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl mt-2 mb-4">The Education to Back It Up</h3>
            <p class="text-tjb-gray leading-relaxed mb-4">
              When a mom asks "what's the evidence for that?" or a provider pushes back, you'll have the answer. The guided walkthrough teaches every option, every tradeoff, and the exact phrases that work.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-tjb-gray space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-tjb-rose-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
                <span>Evidence-based explanations, not opinions</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-tjb-rose-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
                <span>Scripts for difficult conversations</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-tjb-rose-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
                <span>Pass it on — your clients get it free too</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 3 -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
            <img src="/images/doula-holding-hands.webp" srcset="/images/responsive/doula-holding-hands-480w.webp 480w, /images/responsive/doula-holding-hands-960w.webp 960w, /images/doula-holding-hands.webp 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 480px) 480px, (max-width: 960px) 960px, 1024px" alt="Doula holding hands with laboring mother" class="w-full h-64 object-cover" loading="lazy" width="1024" height="1536" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="text-5xl font-bold text-tjb-sage font-serif">03</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl mt-2 mb-4">Pro Mode — Your Practice Operating System</h3>
            <p class="text-tjb-gray leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Stop juggling five apps. Pro Mode gives you one place for client plans, visit notes, scheduling, and simple invoicing — all built around how birth work actually flows.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-tjb-gray space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-tjb-rose-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
                <span>Client birth plans sync automatically from the app</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-tjb-rose-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
                <span>Visit tracking with notes and vitals</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-tjb-rose-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
                <span>Simple invoicing that doesn't require a business degree</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       SOCIAL PROOF — Testimonials
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="bg-tjb-lavender-100 py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <p class="eyebrow mb-4">From New Doulas</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">What Doula's Say After Using These Tools</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
          <blockquote class="text-lg text-tjb-charcoal leading-relaxed italic mb-4">
            "I used to spend 3 hours prepping for every prenatal. Now I open the app, pull up the template, and we're talking about real choices in 20 minutes."
          </blockquote>
          <p class="text-sm text-tjb-gray font-semibold">— Jessica R., doula in training, Austin, TX</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
          <blockquote class="text-lg text-tjb-charcoal leading-relaxed italic mb-4">
            "Pro Mode gave me words I didn't have. When my first client's OB suggested an induction at 38 weeks, I knew exactly what to say."
          </blockquote>
          <p class="text-sm text-tjb-gray font-semibold">— Maria L., new doula, Houston, TX</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       CTA — Download the starter kit
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section id="get-started" class="py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <p class="eyebrow mb-4">Free Starter Kit</p>
      <div class="w-10 h-0.5 bg-tjb-rose-500 mx-auto mb-6"></div>
      <h2 class="mb-5 text-[2.25rem] md:text-[2.75rem] leading-[1.15]">Get the New Doula Starter Kit</h2>
      <p class="text-tjb-gray mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        A curated package of birth plan templates, client onboarding scripts, and a 30-day launch checklist — free when you join the list.
      </p>

      <!-- Brevo form placeholder — wire up when key arrives -->
      <form id="starter-kit-form" class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 max-w-md mx-auto mb-4" action="#" method="POST">
        <input 
          name="email" 
          type="email" 
          placeholder="Your email" 
          class="flex-1 px-5 py-3.5 rounded-full border border-tjb-lavender-300 focus:outline-none focus:border-tjb-rose-400 bg-white transition-colors text-[0.9375rem]"
          required
        />
        <button type="submit" class="btn-primary whitespace-nowrap">
          Get the Kit →
        </button>
      </form>
      <p class="text-xs text-tjb-gray-300">No spam. Just tools, tips, and occasional doula community updates.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       FAQ — Specific to new doulas
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="bg-tjb-cream py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <p class="eyebrow mb-4">Questions</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">Common Questions for New Doulas</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Do I need to be certified to use these tools?</h3>
          <p class="text-tjb-gray">No. The templates and education are useful whether you're certified, in training, or still exploring birth work. Many of our users are volunteer doulas or midwifery students.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">How is this different from other doula business courses?</h3>
          <p class="text-tjb-gray">Most courses teach you how to market yourself. We teach you how to actually serve clients well — with tools that make you look organized, informed, and trustworthy from day one.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Can I share these templates with my clients?</h3>
          <p class="text-tjb-gray">Yes. The birth plan builder in the free app is designed for exactly this. Your clients build their plan, and it syncs to your Pro Mode dashboard. No extra license needed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">What if I'm not tech-savvy?</h3>
          <p class="text-tjb-gray">The app is designed to be simple. If you can use Instagram, you can use this. And Pro Mode walks you through everything step by step.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       FINAL CTA
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="bg-tjb-lavender-100 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to stop feeling like a beginner?</h2>
      <p class="text-tjb-gray mb-8">Join hundreds of new doulas who started with these tools and built real practices.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="#get-started" class="btn-accent">Get the Free Starter Kit</a>
        <a href="/birth-plan-template/" class="btn-secondary">Get the Free App</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
